  <official_title>A Multi-center, Prospective, Randomized Phase III Study of the Safety and Efficacy of R-CEOP-90/R-CEOP-70 Versus R-CHOP-50 in the Treatment of Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma and Follicular Lymphoma Grade 3B</official_title>
