  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of R-CEOP-90/R-CEOP-70
      Versus R-CHOP-50 in the Treatment of Diffuse Large B-cell lymphoma and Follicular Lymphoma
      Grade 3B patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to evaluate the safety and efficacy of R-CEOP-90/R-CEOP-70 Versus R-CHOP-50 in
      the Treatment of Diffuse Large B-cell lymphoma and Follicular Lymphoma Grade 3B patients.
    </textblock>
